title: Abraham Hicks - The Secret Behind The Secret - CD 2
description:
Here is the video \"The Secret Behind The Secret\" - CD2 (AVI format).
The set is composed by several CDs (1, 2, 3 and Extras), where:


* CD1 - It is only a conversation between Esther, Jerry and a reporter.
        It is not so interesting because Abraham didn\&#039;t start speaking yet.


* CD2 - This one (Abraham speaks).


* CD3 - The continuation of CD2 (Abraham speaks).


* CD \"Extras\" - is only a conversation between Esther, Jerry and a reporter, 
                like CD1.
